data.description: This gorgeous home in McAllen is a hidden gem with beautiful features & a great location for the family! This lovely 3,000+ SqFt home includes 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full baths & 2 half baths with plenty of kitchen & dining space too. An amazing feature of this home is the theater room with a wet bar, perfect for relaxing with the family or entertaining guests. Throughout the home are beautiful lighting fixtures in the entryway, dining area, kitchen and recessed lighting throughout for a bright and beautiful home. With all the space this home has to offer, the primary bedroom's closet can't be beat! This walk in closet includes an island, full length mirrors & amazing space in the shelves and cabinets! The backyard includes a covered patio that is perfect for entertaining guests or spending time outside in the gorgeous yard. This home is also located just a few minutes from some great schools in the area and Tres Lagos Park. Don't miss out on this gorgeous hidden gem in McAllen!
